  "notes": "Khalkha Mongolian in Cyrillic script (Mongolia). 7-vowel system with vowel harmony (masculine: a, o, u; feminine: e, ö, ü; neutral: i). Ö = /ø/; Ü = /y/; О = /ɔ/; У = /ʊ/. V → /w/ natively, /v/ in loanwords. Г → /ɣ/ intervocalically.",
